==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Hinduism
<hw>Hinduism</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>the dominant religion
of India; characterized by a caste system anud belief in
reincarnation.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> Hindooism.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>a complex of beliefs and values and customs
including worship of many gods, especially the Trimurti composed of
Brahma the Creator; Vishnu the preserver; and Shiva the
destroyer.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> Hindooism.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

